result.name: Song Cha Xie (Tea House)

reviews.text: Amazing tea selection here. All premium and the tea master serving the tea is extremely experienced and has great knowledge !!!
A very worthwhile experience with knowledgeable and friendly staff who will help you to make the most of a unique experience

Such a wonderful and immersive experience in the true Chinese tea world. The tea lady'service has been truly remarkable. 
It is the perfect gateaway to spend a couple of hours outside the hustle of the city and recharge your energy.

Tea has graced the lives of the Chinese from time immemorial, and is an integral part of everyday life as well as a cultured art of living. The natural unpretentious elegance of taste and fragrance of the tea itself, together with the sophisticated aesthetic of its preparation, makes taking tea more than just refreshment but a liberating experience, especially n this harmonious surroundings where the mind can focus on this gift of delight.

不可多得之品茶地方。
可一面品茶，可一面觀賞其擺設，靜靜為自己充電。

reviews.text:
餐館位於南蓮園池內，環境十分清幽舒適。餐廳內的布置簡單典雅，而且有兩扇大窗，可看到公園外的人工瀑布，令人心曠神宜。
食物方面，用料新鮮講究，能看出精挑細選；而醬料與調味料亦指明使用優質的貨色。每道菜式都精緻好吃，調味恰宜，是素食的好選擇。除了餸菜外，餐廳供應的茶亦很好喝。
餐廳的菜式並不算便宜，但物有所值。要留意餐廳的每個時段都有最低消費要求，但並不難達到。人流亦算多，平日的午市時段亦會滿座。

This vegan restaurant is set amidst a charming Buddhist nunnery/garden, behind a manmade waterfall. Although slightly expensive the food is nicely prepared with fresh ingredients. Worth a visit especially considering the nice setting.
不錯既素食地方，幾有特色，味道亦不錯，連茶都幾好飲，，可惜無可樂果d..
齋菜好吃，环境不錯舒適，只是款式不多和价錢較貴.
Fabulous food. Wonderful service. Friendly staff.
